SUMMARY:Lucky the Leprechaun Hide & Seek
DESCRIPTION:Lucky is back! And this year he brought all his friends with him!\nBetween February 27th and March 17th\, search West Linn’s best hidden places to find Lucky’s hiding spots! \nTurn in your completed Hide & Go Seek booklet to City Hall by March 17th at 3pm to be entered into a raffle! Booklets available online\, outside of City Hall or at select park kiosks beginning February 27.  Open to all ages! \n**There will be no special prize for the first person to turn in their booklet in 2026\, due to March 1 being on a Sunday**
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/lucky-the-leprechaun-hide-seek/2026-03-13/
LOCATION:Oregon
CATEGORIES:Active,Family Fun,Kids Calendar,Outdoor,St. Patrick's
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/lucky-hide-and-seek.jpg
END:VEVENT
