SUMMARY:Gem Faire in Hillsboro
DESCRIPTION:Gem Faire events are open to the public and designed to be welcoming\, educational\, and accessible. \nAt each show\, attendees can explore fine and fashion jewelry\, precious and semi-precious gemstones\, millions of beads\, sparkling crystals\, gold and silver\, tools\, supplies\, and display materials—all under one roof. \nGem Faire offers an opportunity to discover new materials\, connect with knowledgeable vendors\, and experience the gem and jewelry industry firsthand. \nAdmission $7 weekend pass | Purchase tickets at the door | Free for children 11 & under.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/gem-faire-in-hillsboro/2026-03-13/
